entity.name: COVID-19: Public health updates
entity.description: Information on how to take care of yourself and others from authorities and public officials.

text:
The COVID alert level in the UK has moved from 4 to 3. 

The government's plan is working and we are containing the spread of coronavirus. Thank you to everyone for following the rules and playing their part - we must keep going to keep the level down.

#StayAlert https://t.co/leYq3NSE41
